Welcome to the=C2=A0990=C2=A0newly Not Boring people=C2=A0who have joined u=
s since last Tuesday! If you haven=E2=80=99t subscribed, join=C2=A0185,857 =
smart, curious folks by subscribing here:
Hi friends =F0=9F=91=8B,
Happy Tuesday, Happy Valentine=E2=80=99s Day =E2=80=94 love you all =E2=80=
=94 and an extra special Happy Valentine=E2=80=99s Day to Puja =F0=9F=98=8D
We=E2=80=99re still reeling from the Eagles=E2=80=99 Super Bowl loss over h=
ere at Not Boring HQ, so we decided to turn up the optimism dial to 11 to c=
ombat the sting.=20
Today, Rahul Rana [ https://substack.com/redirect/4f1ae954-d2f9-44f4-a31f-0=
e782fac9852?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkR=
NpU ] makes the case that we need more techno-optimistic storytelling =E2=
=80=94 sci-fi, movies, art, monuments, and fairs that paint a compelling vi=
sion of the future. Good Stories can inspire founders to tackle big challen=
ges and help people make sense of the dizzying pace of technological advanc=
e in a way that research papers can=E2=80=99t. Rahul dives into the Golden =
Age of Sci-Fi (1930s - 1960s) to pull out lessons that are more relevant th=
an ever in an increasingly complex and decentralized world.=20
You might remember Rahul from the essay he wrote in July, Making Moonshots =
[ https://substack.com/redirect/95a20620-aab8-4209-97fe-db39c7086dcf?j=3Dey=
J1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ]. Rahul is No=
t Boring=E2=80=99s Atoms Research Analyst. Still a college senior (double-m=
ajoring in finance and astrophysics), Rahul has interned at Lux Capital and=
 General Atlantic, worked on building the bio research organization Arcadia=
 Science [ https://substack.com/redirect/c1447551-b5b8-435e-b423-1a98f714d3=
ca?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ], an=
d wrote a book also titled Making Moonshots [ https://substack.com/redirect=
/9e99b7b0-6963-4332-925e-c868db40ea85?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlN=
uaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ]. His mission is to bring the frontier to li=
fe, and I=E2=80=99m excited for him to explain why stories are such an impo=
rtant piece of that puzzle. =20
Let=E2=80=99s get to it.
Today=E2=80=99s Not Boring is brought to you by=E2=80=A6 Fount [ https://su=
bstack.com/redirect/e510293d-f301-4255-9902-f0e1f3cf788e?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3=
QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ]
Fount Pro [ https://substack.com/redirect/e510293d-f301-4255-9902-f0e1f3cf7=
88e?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ] is=
 a personalized health and performance program for people who want to get t=
he most out of themselves.=20
The brainchild of Andrew Herr, who ran ran human performance efforts for th=
e US military and designed programs for Navy SEALs and fighter pilots, Foun=
t analyzes your body with cutting edge technology and protocols, sets you u=
p with a team to personalize and guide your plan (my coach is an ex-Navy SE=
AL), and designs a plan you=E2=80=99ll actually stick with.=20
I=E2=80=99ve been on the Fount program for about a year and a half, and it=
=E2=80=99s been a complete game changer. When I wrote about Fount [ https:/=
/substack.com/redirect/f6cf9a38-1b64-4f0e-a954-4df73ecba77b?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXA=
wZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ] last March, I mention=
ed that my goals were to improve my focus, energy, and stress, and that it =
worked: they discovered and fixed my anemia,  got my B-12, omega-3, testost=
erone, and fasting blood sugar in line, and gave me my energy back. Since t=
hen, I asked Fount to help me get back in shape. One year and another kid l=
ater, I=E2=80=99m 33 lbs lighter, my VO2 max increased from 38 to 53, my HR=
V hit an all-time high, and I=E2=80=99m running at below a 6:30/mile pace c=
onsistently.
Simply put: Fount Pro works. Whether you want to improve your energy and fo=
cus, get back in shape, manage the stress of a high-pressure job, or increa=
se your longevity, the Fount team designs a plan that works for you specifi=
cally. Fount isn=E2=80=99t cheap, but you get what you pay for. It=E2=80=99=
s the single highest-ROI thing I=E2=80=99ve done for my performance.
Book a free consult with one of their world-class performance advisors at t=
