4798-b6a1-7f489aa431aa?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqO=
sa8-6m8ExkRNpU ], Balaji puts the onus back on the technologists themselves=
=2E
We need to take time out of our busy days to make the case, repeatedly and =
with high production values, that technological progress is the most import=
ant thing we can do for broad-based prosperity and economic growth, and for=
