a command-and-control management system is a little like trying to run a mo=
dern economy out of a Politburo. Letting them work toward an agreed-on goal=
 is something more like a free and largely self-coordinated market of ideas=
=2E=C2=A0
Stephenson=E2=80=99s take challenges writers, poets, filmmakers, and other =
creatives to start pulling their weight and supplying big visions that help=
